In the video the woman can be seen trying to drive away as the man knocks on her window. JOHANNESBURG - A video showing a woman being harassed while trying to drive off in the Pretoria CBD has caused outrage on social media. In the short clip posted on Wednesday, the woman can be heard screaming for the man to move away from her car. READ: Man arrested over homeless attack released After a few seconds the man can be seen reaching for the top of the car where he allegedly takes the radio aerial. The incident, which allegedly took place on Francis Baard Street, has caused a stir on social media with many people calling for justice on behalf of the woman.